<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You're Invited to Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .benefit-box {
            background-color: #f0f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You're Invited!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hey!</h2>

            <p><strong>
                    <%= referrerName %>
                </strong> thinks you'd love Engagematic and invited you to try it!</p>

            <div class="badge">
                Special Offer: <%= extendedTrialDays %>-Day Extended Trial
            </div>

            <p>Engagematic is the #1 AI-powered LinkedIn content generator trusted by thousands of professionals to:
            </p>

            <div class="benefit-box">
                <strong style="color: #667eea;">Create Engaging Posts in 30 Seconds</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Stop staring at blank screens. Our AI writes perfect
                    LinkedIn posts for you.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-box">
                <strong style="color: #667eea;">Custom AI Personas</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Train AI to write in YOUR voice. Authentic content, every
                    time.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-box">
                <strong style="color: #667eea;">Advanced Analytics</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #666;">Track performance and optimize your LinkedIn strategy.</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Your Special Perks:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><%= extendedTrialDays %> days FREE trial (double the normal trial!)</li>
                <li>Full access to all features</li>
                <li>No credit card required</li>
                <li>Cancel anytime</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= referralLink %>" class="cta-button">
                    Start My <%= extendedTrialDays %>-Day Trial â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
                By clicking the button above, you'll get <%= extendedTrialDays %> days to explore all features for free.
            </p>

            <div
                style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #e65100;">Why <%= referrerName %> Loves Engagematic:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #e65100;">Join thousands of professionals who've saved 10+ hours
                    per week while growing their LinkedIn presence by 300%!</p>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">See you inside!<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>